  <Docs>
    <summary>Specifies the position of a single variation axis when customizing a variable font.</summary>
    <remarks><format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[
## Remarks

<xref:T:SkiaSharp.SKFontVariationPositionCoordinate> is used with <xref:P:SkiaSharp.SKFontArguments.VariationDesignPosition> to specify particular values for variation axes when cloning a typeface.

## Examples

```csharp
var coord = new SKFontVariationPositionCoordinate
{
    Axis = SKFourByteTag.Parse("wght"),
    Value = 700,
};
```
]]></format></remarks>
